<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
      .header { background: #007bff; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
      .content { padding: 20px; background: #f8f9fa; }
      .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; margin: 10px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; }
      .btn-approve { background: #28a745; color: white; }
      .btn-reject { background: #dc3545; color: white; }
      .info-box { background: #e9ecef; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 15px 0; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>🛡️ Parental Consent Required</h1>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello Parent/Guardian,</h2>
        
        <p>Your child <strong><%= @user.first_name %> <%= @user.last_name %></strong> has requested to create an account on our platform.</p>
        
        <div class="info-box">
          <h3>📋 Child's Information:</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Name:</strong> <%= @user.first_name %> <%= @user.last_name %></li>
            <li><strong>Email:</strong> <%= @user.email %></li>
            <li><strong>Age:</strong> <%= @user.age %> years old</li>
            <li><strong>Birth Date:</strong> <%= @user.birth_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
          <h3>🎯 Platform Features:</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Join educational organizations</li>
            <li>Participate in age-appropriate activities</li>
            <li>Connect with peers in supervised environments</li>
            <li>Access to parental oversight features</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
          <h3>⚠️ Important Information:</h3>
          <p>By approving this consent, you acknowledge that:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Your child will be able to join organizations on our platform</li>
            <li>All activities are supervised and age-appropriate</li>
            <li>You can revoke consent at any time by contacting support</li>
            <li>Your child's data will be handled according to our privacy policy</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
          <a href="<%= @consent_url %>" class="button btn-approve">✅ Approve Consent</a>
          <a href="<%= @consent_url %>" class="button btn-reject">❌ View Options</a>
        </div>

        <p><small>This consent link is secure and unique to your child's account. If you did not expect this email, please ignore it.</small></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html> 